quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  20,111,"Kandi uburanga bwose (ku munsi w’imperuka) buzaba bwaciye bugufi imbere ya (Allah), Uhoraho akanabeshaho ibiriho byose. Kandi inkozi z’ibibi zizaba ziri mu kaga"
  20,112,"N’ukora ibyiza kandi ari umwemera, ntazigera atinya kurenganywa cyangwa kwamburwa (ibyiza yakoze)"
  20,113,"Uko ni ko twahishuye Qur’an mu rurimi rw’Icyarabu, tunayisobanuramo ibibaburira kugira ngo barusheho kugandukira (Allah) cyangwa bibahe kwibuka"
  20,114,"Ku bw’ibyo, uri hejuru ya byose ni Allah, ubutungane ni ubwe, Umwami w’ukuri. Bityo (yewe Muhamadi) ntukagire ubwira (mu kwakira) Qur’an mbere y’uko kuyiguhishurira birangira. Ahubwo ujye uvuga uti “Nyagasani wanjye! Nyongerera ubumenyi.”"
  20,115,"Kandi rwose mbere twari twarahaye Adamu isezerano (ryo kutarya ku giti cyo mu ijuru), ariko yaribagiwe (akiryaho), ntitwigeze tumusangana ukutagamburuzwa"
  20,116,"Unibuke ubwo twabwiraga abamalayika tuti “Mwubamire Adamu!” Nuko barubama, uretse Ibilisi (Shitani) wabyanze"
  20,117,"Nuko turavuga tuti “Yewe Adamu! Mu by’ukuri uyu ni umwanzi wawe, wowe n’umugore wawe. Bityo, muramenye ntazabakure mu ijuru mutazavaho mukagorwa.”"
  20,118,Mu by’ukuri nta nzara uzarigiriramo ndetse nta n’ubwo uzariburiramo icyo kwambara
  20,119,Kandi nta nyota uzarigiriramo ndetse nta n’ubwo uzicwa n’izuba
  20,120,Nuko Shitani imwoshya igira iti “Yewe Adamu! Ese nkurangire igiti waryaho ukazabaho iteka ndetse ukazanagira ubwami budashira?”
  20,121,"Nuko bombi (Adamu na Hawa) bakiryaho maze ubwambure bwabo burabagaragarira, bityo batangira kubutwikiriza amababi (y’ibiti) byo mu busitani bwo mu Ijuru. Nuko Adamu aba acumuye kuri Nyagasani we, maze arayoba"
  20,122,"Hanyuma Nyagasani we aramutoranya, yakira ukwicuza kwe aranamuyobora"
  20,123,"(Allah) aravuga ati “Nimumanuke mwembi murivemo (mujye ku isi), bamwe muri mwe ari abanzi b’abandi (abantu bazaba abanzi ba Shitani, ndetse na we abe umwanzi wabo). Kandi umuyoboro wanjye nuramuka ubagezeho, uzakurikira uwo muyoboro wanjye ntazigera ayoba cyangwa ngo agorwe.”"
  20,124,"Ariko uzirengagiza urwibutso rwanjye, mu by’ukuri azagira ubuzima bw’inzitane ndetse no ku munsi w’imperuka tuzamuzura ari impumyi.”"
  20,125,Azavuga ati “Nyagasani wanjye! Ni kuki unzuye ndi impumyi kandi (ku isi) narabonaga?”
  20,126,"(Allah) azavuga ati “Uko ni ko bigomba kumera, (kuko) ibimenyetso byacu byakugezeho ukabyiyibagiza; none nawe uyu munsi uribagiranye"
  20,127,Uko ni na ko duhana uwarengereye ntiyemere ibimenyetso bya Nyagasani we. Kandi rwose ibihano byo ku munsi w’imperuka ni byo bikaze ndetse bizahoraho
  20,128,"Ese kuba twaroretse ibisekuru byinshi mbere yabo, bakaba banyura mu matongo yabo ntibibaha kuyoboka? Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo inyigisho ku bantu bafite ubwenge.”"
  20,129,"Kandi iyo bitaza kuba ijambo ryaturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe ryabanje (ryo kudahaniraho) ndetse ntihanabeho igihe cyagenwe (cyo guhanwa), byari kuba ihame ko bacirwaho iteka (hano ku isi)"
  20,130,"Bityo, ujye wihanganira ibyo bavuga (yewe Muhamadi), unatagatifuze Nyagasani wawe umukuza mbere y’uko izuba rirasa na mbere y’uko rirenga, ndetse ujye unamutagatifuza umukuza mu bihe by’ijoro no mu mpera z’amanywa; kugira ngo uzagire ibyishimo (by’ingororano za Nyagasani)"
  20,131,"Kandi ntuzarambure amaso yawe urangamira ibyo twahaye amatsinda anyuranye muri bo (ababangikanyamana) kugira ngo bishimishe, (kuko) ari imitako y’ubuzima bw’isi (twabahaye) ngo tuyibageragereshe. Kandi ingororano Nyagasani wawe azatanga (mu ijuru) ni zo nziza ndetse zizahoraho"
  20,132,"Kandi ujye ubwiriza abo mu rugo iwawe gusali ndetse unabihozeho. Ntitujya tugusaba amafunguro, kuko ari twe tuyaguha. Kandi iherezo ryiza ni iry’abagandukira (Allah)"
  20,133,(Abahakanye) baravuga bati “Kuki (Muhamadi) atatuzanira igitangaza giturutse kwa Nyagasani we?” Ese ntibagezweho n’igitangaza (Qur’an) gishimangira ibyavuzwe mu bitabo byabanje
  20,134,"N’iyo tuza kubarimbuza ibihano mbere ye (Muhamadi), mu by’ukuri bari kuvuga bati “Nyagasani wacu! Iyo uza kutwoherereza intumwa, twari gukurikira amagambo yawe mbere y’uko dusuzugurika ngo tunasebe.”"
  20,135,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Buri wese arategereje, bityo namwe nimutegereze, muzamenya abari mu nzira igororotse kandi bayobotse.”"